# API Server Configuration for Frontend

## Local Development

```bash
# .env.local (create this file in app/ directory)
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:4000
```

## Production

```bash
# .env.production (create this file in app/ directory)
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://your-production-api.com
```

## Usage in App

```typescript
const API_URL = process.env.EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL || 'http://localhost:4000';

// Fetching videos
const response = await fetch(`${API_URL}/api/videos`);
const videos = await response.json();

// Creating a video
await fetch(`${API_URL}/api/videos`, {
  method: 'POST',
  headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
  body: JSON.stringify({
    title: 'My Video',
    fileName: 'video.mp4',
    templateId: 'khatereh',
    duration: 15,
    thumbnailUri: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,...',
    contentBase64: 'data:video/mp4;base64,...'
  })
});
```
